hopobject.body: Very funny pictures murad resurgence toner -Merritt Wever's acceptance speech: The first award of the night was a major upset, and its winner appeared to be just as surprised as we were. Accepting the outstanding supporting actress award for her role on "Nurse Jackie," Wever simply said, "Thanks so much. Thank you so much. I gotta go. Bye," and scurried off the stage. Even if those who don't watch "Nurse Jackie" can appreciate Wever's brevity, particularly for an awards show that usually runs overtime.
